    <item>
      <title>随着加密资产上涨，纳斯达克准备上市现货比特币 ETF 期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/nasdaq-poised-to-list-spot-bitcoin-etf-options-amid-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克公司计划最早于周二在贝莱德公司的比特币交易所交易基金上推出期权，允许投资者使用衍生品押注或做空全球最大的数字资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/nasdaq-poised-to-list-spot-bitcoin-etf-options-amid-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
