      <title>赞比亚、津巴布韦部长称卡里巴水坝水位暴跌，两国面临警钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/water-plunge-at-kariba-dam-wake-up-call-for-zambia-zimbabwe-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，世界最大人工水库水位暴跌，导致赞比亚和津巴布韦停电数小时，这表明两国需要实现能源来源多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/water-plunge-at-kariba-dam-wake-up-call-for-zambia-zimbabwe-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 18:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
